Class GraphNavKeys

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
KeyListener, MouseListener, EventListener
public class GraphNavKeys
extends Object
implements KeyListener, MouseListener

The GraphNavKeys class allows for the arrow keys and the mouse to be used to navigate the graph.
